casebody.data:
Kimberly O'TOOLE, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Francesco PICCIRILLO, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2263 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 21, 2017 SALTER, EMAS and FERNANDEZ, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of certiorari, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
